@startuml
actor User
participant "Frontend (UI)" as UI
participant "Backend (API)" as API
database Database

User -> UI: Enter search query
UI -> API: Send search request
API -> Database: Fetch matching stocks
Database --> API: Return stock list
API -> UI: Display stock list
User -> UI: Sort stock list (e.g., by price or name)
UI -> API: Send sort request
API -> UI: Display sorted stock list
User -> UI: Select stock to view details
UI -> API: Request stock details
API -> Database: Fetch stock information
Database --> API: Return stock details
API -> UI: Display stock details
alt Add to Portfolio
    User -> UI: Select "Add to Portfolio"
    UI -> API: Add stock to portfolio
    API -> Database: Update portfolio
    Database --> API: Portfolio updated
    API -> UI: Confirm addition
    UI --> User: Show success message
else Create Notification
    User -> UI: Select "Create Notification"
    UI -> API: Set notification for stock
    API -> Database: Save notification details
    Database --> API: Notification saved
    API -> UI: Confirm notification creation
    UI --> User: Show success message
end
@enduml
